C%22%3Eyouvetsi%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20perfect%20when%20you%20need%20a%20quick%20pasta%20dish%2C%20and%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-greek-pasta-dish-thats-better-than-lasagna-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Epastitsio%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20like%20the%20Greek%20version%20of%20lasagna%20%E2%80%94%20but%20better.%20His%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreek-avgolemono-soup-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eavgolemono%20soup%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20ultimate%20sick%20day%20cure%2C%20and%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-authentic-greek-baklava-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaklava%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20my%20favorite%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20summer%20tomato%20season%20is%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20my%20dad%20loves%20whipping%20up%20yemista.%20It's%20light%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20comforting%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20always%20request%20it%20whenever%20I%20visit%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20to%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYemista%20was%20one%20of%20the%20many%20Greek%20dishes%20I%20grew%20up%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta's%20dad%20with%20his%20Greek%20meatballs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649124b951ea980019d6d008%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20dad%20with%20his%20famous%20Greek%20meatballs.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20yemista%20means%20%26quot%3Bstuffed%26quot%3B%20in%20Greek.%20True%20to%20its%20name%2C%20the%20dish%20traditionally%20consists%20of%20tomatoes%20and%20bell%20peppers%20stuffed%20with%20rice%20and%20ground%20beef%20and%20baked%20in%20the%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYemista%20(also%20spelled%20gemista)%20was%20a%20weekly%20staple%20of%20my%20childhood.%20My%20parents%20immigrated%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Greece%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20loved%20whipping%20up%20the%20dishes%20they%20grew%20up%20with%20for%20my%20sister%20and%20me.%20Their%20food%20helped%20me%20connect%20to%20my%20culture%20as%20a%20first-generation%20Greek%20American%20and%20instilled%20an%20early%20and%20enduring%20love%20for%20Mediterranean%20cooking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20%E2%80%94%20an%20excellent%20home%20cook%20%E2%80%94%20has%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20make%20many%20classic%20Greek%20dishes.%20And%20he%20thinks%20his%20yemista%20is%20perfect%20for%20a%20summer%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20dad's%20yemista%20only%20needs%20a%20few%20simple%20ingredients.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ingredients%20for%20Anneta's%20Dad's%20Yemista%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6318d81f5a0e5a0018d2ed2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20dad's%20yemista%20features%20tomatoes%2C%20ground%20beef%2C%20and%20parsley.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20yemista%20at%20home%2C%20you'll%20need%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E8%20(relatively%20large)%20tomatoes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20pound%20of%20ground%20beef%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BD%20onion%2C%20chopped%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%E2%85%94%20cup%20of%20rice%20(we%20use%20the%20medium-grain%20Calrose%20rice)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BE%20cup%20of%20parsley%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20clove%20of%20garlic%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20yemista%20is%20traditionally%20made%20with%20both%20tomatoes%20and%20bell%20peppers%2C%20my%20dad%20has%20found%20that%20bell%20peppers%20in%20the%20US%20are%20thicker%20than%20they%20are%20in%20Greece%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thus%20trickier%20to%20cook%20evenly%20with%20the%20tomatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20often%20just%20makes%20yemista%20with%20tomatoes%20now