20time%20I'm%20somehow%20even%20more%20exhausted%2C%20confused%2C%20and%20overwhelmed.%20Instead%20of%20dealing%20with%20potty%20training%20and%20tantrums%2C%20I'm%20dealing%20with%20teen%20drivers%2C%20volatile%20emotions%2C%20and%20big%20life%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20frustrated%20and%20guilty%2C%20like%20I'm%20doing%20something%20wrong%20for%20somehow%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-wasnt-prepared-for-how-expensive-teenage-years-can-be-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20productive%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20older%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20part%20of%20it%20is%20that%20when%20they%20were%20small%2C%20there%20was%20a%20routine%20that%20let%20me%20get%20some%20work%20done.%20There%20were%20daily%20nap%20times%20I%20could%20count%20on%2C%20movies%20I%20could%20turn%20on%2C%20or%20playdates%20I%20could%20schedule.%20But%20with%20teens%2C%20I%20am%20never%20off%20the%20clock.%20I'm%20always%20a%20text%20away%2C%20and%20with%20a%20teen%20driver%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20can't%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20available%2024%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20older%20kids%20take%20up%20more%20space%2C%20are%20louder%2C%20and%20have%20more%20intense%20needs%20than%20I%20anticipated.%20Every%20day%20feels%20like%20a%20circus%20show%20of%20juggling%2C%20and%20I'm%20kind%20of%20holding%20my%20breath%20and%20hoping%20I'll%20have%20enough%20breathing%20room%20to%20manage%20any%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20cartoon%20and%20snuggles%20could%20suffice%20with%20a%20toddler%2C%20teenagers%20require%2050%20memes%2C%20a%20thoughtful%20conversation%2C%20and%20probably%20Chick-fil-A%20to%20connect.%20I%20feel%20a%20pressure%20to%20be%20emotionally%20available%20in%20a%20way%20I%20didn't%20when%20they%20were%20younger%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20switch%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20work%20mode%20when%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231275bfd-1090-438c-a950