.com%2Fscientist-studies-ultra-processed-foods-rules-to-stop-overeating-simple-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efoods%20in%20moderation%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20to%20prevent%20the%20%26quot%3Ball%20or%20nothing%26quot%3B%20mindset%20that's%20among%20the%20most%20common%20reasons%20that%20weight%20loss%20diets%20fail%2C%20said%20Tara%20Schmidt%2C%20lead%20dietitian%20for%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDieters%20often%20%26quot%3Bget%20into%20very%20black%20and%20white%20thinking%26quot%3B%20when%20trying%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20Schmidt%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20really%20no%20wiggle%20room.%20People%20get%20trapped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F39826856%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20dieters%20had%20fewer%20cravings%20and%20more%20weight%20loss%20over%20a%20year%2C%20and%20maintained%20it%20the%20following%20year%2C%20if%20they%20included%20small%20portions%20treat%20foods%2C%20like%20cake%20or%20burgers%2C%20as%20part%20of%20balanced%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%20excluding%20them%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20support%20what%20dietitians%20are%20always%20trying%20to%20tell%20their%20patients%3A%20a%20flexible%20diet%20approach%20is%20much%20better%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lose-weight-by-eating-more-according-to-dietitians-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweight%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Schmidt%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAllowing%20for%20a%20balanced%20way%20of%20including%20your%20favorite%20foods%2C%20a%20planned%20indulgence%2C%20really%20helps%20people%20feel%20less%20deprived%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5c407a1-1140-4c49-92cc-e10276b81393%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20treat%20yourself%20and%20still%20lose%20weight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%