r%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F444103%2Flgbtq-representation-indian-cinema-ott-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETherapy%2C%20of%20course%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20with%20the%20individual.%3C%2Fa%3E%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20family%20is%20the%20first%2C%20and%20sometimes%20deepest%2C%20site%20of%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFamilies%20can%20be%20the%20biggest%20oppressors%2C%20often%20reflecting%20generational%20trauma%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Akanksha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20starts%20with%20conditional%20love%20%E2%80%94%20the%20idea%20that%20you%E2%80%99ll%20only%20be%20accepted%20if%20you%20suppress%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pressure%20can%20manifest%20in%20horrific%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20are%20forced%20into%20marriages%20where%20their%20identities%20are%20hidden%2C%20causing%20trauma%20not%20just%20to%20themselves%20but%20also%20their%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20wounds%20are%20passed%20down.%20Healing%20begins%20by%20naming%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssertiveness%20training%2C%20boundary-making%2C%20and%20building%20chosen%20families%20become%20critical%20tools.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20helps%20to%20give%20them%20platforms%2C%20online%20or%20offline%2C%20where%20they%20feel%20seen.%20Sometimes%2C%20social%20media%20becomes%20a%20lifeline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Assertive%20training%20is%20a%20structured%20approach%20to%20helping%20individuals%20communicate%20more%20effectively%20by%20expressing%20their%20thoughts%2C%20feelings%2C%20and%20needs%20clearly%2C%20confidently%2C%20and%20respectfully.%20It%20is%20designed%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20passivity%20and%20aggression%2C%20thus%2C%20enabling%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20themselves.%20Whether%20in%20personal%20relationships%20or%20professional%20settings%2C%20assertiveness%20is%20about%20being%20honest%20and%20direct%20while%20maintaining%20respect%20and%20empathy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20assertiveness%20training%20teaches%20people%20how%20to%20say%20%E2%80%9Cno%E2%80%9D%20without%20guilt%2C%20express%20opinions%20without%20fear%2C%20handle%20criticism%20constructively%2C%20and%20set%20healthy%20personal%20and%20professional%20boundaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAssertiveness%20training%20is%20frequently%20incorporated%20into%20therapeutic%20contexts%20such%20as%20Cognitive%20Behavioural%20Therapy%20(CBT)%2C%20social%20skills%20groups%2C%20and%20trauma%20recovery%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Dr%20Bhargava%20shares%20the%20story%20of%20a%20patient%20from%20the%20queer%20community%20diagnosed%20with%20Generalised%20Anxiety%20Disorder.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20evaluation%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20gender-related%20confusion%20and%20societal%20pressure%20in%20adolescence%20played%20a%20huge%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETreatment%20involved%20more%20than%20just%20medication.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20initiated%20a%20personalised%20psychosocial%20intervention%20focused%20on%20tackling%20internalised%20helplessness%20and%20cognitive%20distortions.%20It%20was%20about%20building%20resilience%20and%20not%20erasing%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20mental%20health%20care%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20specialty%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%20of%20inclusive%20practice.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-96-1750328434-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451943%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EQueer%20mental%20health%20care%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20specialty%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%20of%20inclusive%20practice.%20Picture%20source%3A%20SpringerLink%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20queer%20mental%20health%20care%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20specialty%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%20of%20inclusive%20practice.%20%E2%80%9CStandard%20care%20guidelines%20today%20emphasise%20empathetic%2C%20non-judgmental%2C%20inclusive%20approaches.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20baseline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Generalised%20Anxiety%20Disorder%20(GAD)%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20condition%20marked%20by%20excessive%2C%20persistent%20worry%20about%20various%20aspects%20of%20life%20such%20as%20health%2C%20work%2C%20relationships%2C%20or%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20queer%20individuals%2C%20this%20anxiety%20can%20be%20intensified%20by%20systemic%20discrimination%2C%20societal%20stigma%2C%20and%20internalized%20stressors%20related%20to%20their%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPersonalised%20psychosocial%20interventions%20are%20customised%20mental%20health%20and%20support%20strategies%20that%20address%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20unique%20psychological%2C%20emotional%2C%20social%2C%20and%20sometimes%20cultural%20needs.%20Rather%20than%20using%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%2C%20these%20interventions%20are%20tailored%20to%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20specific%20circumstances%2C%20identity%2C%20life%20experiences%2C%20and%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20involves%20introducing%20the%20individual%20to%20queer%20support%20groups%20and%20building%20coping%20skills%20against%20anxiety%20and%20suicidal%20thoughts%20through%20meditation%20and%20other%20related%20activities.%20It%20can%20also%20sometimes%20involve%20having%20open%20conversations%20in%20family%20therapy%20sessions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20pride%20comes%20with%20a%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20can%20be%20done%3F%20Dr%20Akanksha%20suggests%20it%20begins%20starting%20a%20conversation.%20Creating%20a%20safe%20space%20grounded%20in%20empathy%20and%20care%20whether%20at%20home%2C%20within%20communities%2C%20or%20among%20allies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaces%20like%20The%20Humsafar%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhumsafar.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESahyog%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20already%20leading%20the%20way.%20Beyond%20offering%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20the%20clinic%20provides%20holistic%20services%20ranging%20from%20nutrition%20guidance%20and%20care%20against%20Sexually%20Transmitted%20Infections%20to%20counselling%20and%20legal%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmanochikitsa.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManochikitsa%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%20provides%20online%20LGBTQ%2B%20counselling%20with%20licensed%20psychologists%2C%20offering%20services%20in%20multiple%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Falternativestory.in%2Fservices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Alternative%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20queer-affirma