erything%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20planning%20process%2C%20Namita%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CSustainability%20was%20at%20the%20core%20of%20everything.%20We%20had%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20everything%20we%20planned%20resonated%20with%20our%20values.%20We%20knew%20we%20did%20not%20want%20excess%20plastic%2C%20unnecessary%20waste%2C%20or%20carbon%20emissions%20at%20our%20celebration.%20Every%20decision%20was%20directed%20towards%20reducing%20our%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20couple%20prioritised%20reducing%20waste.%20Invitations%20were%20predominantly%20digital%2C%20with%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20printed%20invites%20sent%20only%20to%20older%20family%20members%20who%20were%20not%20familiar%20with%20digital%20cards.%20These%20were%20crafted%20on%20uncoated%20recycled%20paper%2C%20with%20seed%20paper%20envelopes%20that%20guests%20could%20later%20plant%20to%20grow%20flowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bride%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20dress%20was%20another%20symbol%20of%20her%20commitment%20to%20sustainability.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wedding%20sari%20was%20a%20beautiful%20handloom%20piece.%20It%20was%20customised%20with%20appliqu%C3%A9%20embroidery%20made%20from%20scrap%20fabric%20and%20tassels%20made%20from%20%E2%80%98manjadikuru%E2%80%99%20seeds%2C%20which%20were%20handcrafted%20by%20women%20in%20Auroville.%20It%20supported%20local%20artisans%2C%20slow%20fashion%2C%20and%20environmental%20consciousness%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Namita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theme%20of%20upcycling%20ran%20throughout%20the%20entire%20celebration.%20Avinash%E2%80%99s%20mehndi%20and%20haldi%20kurtas%20were%20made%20from%20his%20