d-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAvinash%20and%20Namita%20used%20fresh%20flowers%20as%20part%20of%20the%20decoration%20for%20all%20the%20wedding%20events%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20also%20helped%20the%20couple%20in%20planning%20the%20low-waste%20wedding.%20The%20bride%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Priya%20Manohar%20(55)%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20planning%20such%20an%20unconventional%20wedding%20felt%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20courage%20and%20belief%20that%20it%20was%20possible%20put%20all%20our%20fears%20to%20rest.%20We%20broke%20down%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20looking%20at%20each%20element%20individually%2C%20considering%20what%20was%20really%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20upcycling%20unused%20saris%20into%20statement%20outfits%20to%20avoiding%20plastic%20in%20the%20decor%20or%20for%20consumables%20like%20water%2C%20every%20detail%20was%20carefully%20planned.%20We%20used%20cruelty-free%20products%20for%20bridal%20makeup.%20We%20also%20used%20palm%20leaf%20straws%20for%20the%20coco