ng%20waste%20collectors%2C%20transporters%2C%20and%20tech%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20daily%20basis%20our%20rate%20card%20gets%20updated%20on%20our%20application%20as%20per%20market%20rates.%20For%20example%2C%20today%20we%20offer%20Rs%2011%20per%20kg%20of%20rupees%20for%20an%20old%20newspaper%2C%20which%20is%20competitive%20with%20local%20scrap%20dealers%20as%20well.%20In%20this%20business%2C%20accurate%20weight%20is%20far%20more%20important%20than%20higher%20rates.%20We%20always%20use%20well-calibrated%20electronic%20weighing%20scales%20and%20assure%20money%20for%20every%20gram%20to%20the%20customer%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founders%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETech%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20trackability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20built%20with%20the%20end-user%20in%20mind.%20Customers%20can%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESchedule%20pickups%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrack%20waste%20weights%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGet%20digital%20receipts%20and%20payments%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EView%20history%20of%20transactions%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%2C%20Scrapdeal%20uses%20data%20analytics%20and%20optimised%20routing%20to%20reduce%20fuel%20consumption%20and%20emissions.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20rare%20blend%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F426765%2Ffive-watershed-important-moments-india-environment-chipko-green-courts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmental%20consciousness%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20operational%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDKrh0KyM3-R%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDKrh0KyM3-R%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%