ople%E2%80%99s%20health%20concerns.%20Of%20course%2C%20these%20products%20weren%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20tasty%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20people%20understood%20that%20they%20were%20making%20a%20health-conscious%20choice%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20our%20business%20started%20to%20gain%20momentum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ramakiran%2C%20Bachelor%20of%20Ayurvedic%20Medicine%20and%20Surgery%2C%20Doctor%20of%20Medicine%20(Ayurveda)%2C%20Post%20Graduate%20Certificate%20in%20Kidney%20Sciences%2C%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plant-based%20protein%20supplements%20contain%20no%20unnecessary%20additives%2C%20and%20what%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20the%20carefully%20crafted%20herbal%20blend.%20This%20formulation%2C%20developed%20by%20a%20team%20of%20experts%2C%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20support%20digestion.%20Each%20batch%20also%20goes%20through%20lab%20testing%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20potency.%20The%20combination%20of%20high-quality%20ingredients%20and%20scientific%20expertise%20makes%20this%20protein%20not%20just%20effective%20but%20also%20a%20safe%20option.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nidhi%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20fertility%20specialist%20in%20Noida%2C%20with%20over%2012%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPCOS%20is%20a%20multifactorial%20disorder%20that%20affects%20our%20metabolism%20and%20can%20cause%20diabetes%2C%20obesity%2C%20and%20other%20health%20problems.%20While%20PCOS%20itself%20does%20not%20directly%20cause%20inflammation%2C%20it%20causes%20obesity%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20leads%20to%20inflammation%20in%20the%20body.%E2%80%9D%20She%20recommends%20incorporating%20anti-inflammatory%20foods%20like%20herbal%20blends%20such%20as%20ginger%2C%20turmeric%2C%20and%20fenugreek%20to%20help%20manage%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20observes%20that%20many%20patients%20are%20shifting%20to%20plant-based%20protein%20due%20to%20its%20benefits%20in%20managing%20cholesterol.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20many%20patients%20switching%20to%20plant-based%20protein%20and%20now%2C%20they%20feel%20healthier%20and%20robust%2C%20and%20their%20cholesterol%20levels%20are%20also%20controlled%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20more%20studies%20are%20needed%20to%20prove%20this%2C%20it%20is%20the%20experiences%20of%20people%20that%20help%20to%20understand%20that%20this%20can%20be%20helpful.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T203517.232_11zon-1750172728.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cosmix%20uses%20real%20ingredients%20such%20as%20vanilla%20beans%20and%20cocoa%20powder%20to%20make%20the%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T203517.232_11zon-1750172728.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T203517.232_11zon-1750172728-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-17T203517.232_11zon-1750172728-500x262.jp